        public static long getCRC​(java.util.ArrayList<java.lang.Long> rawData,
                          BesCalc_CRC.crcMode crcMode)
        Calculate CRC checksum.
        Parameters:
        rawData - Data to be used to calculate CRC checksum in ArrayList type
        crcMode - CRC mode
        The options are: CRC4_ITU,CRC8,CRC16_CCITT,CRC32,...
        Returns:
        CRC value in long type

      • getCRC

        public static long getCRC​(java.util.ArrayList<java.lang.Long> rawData,
                          long poly,
                          long crcInit,
                          long crcXOROUT,
                          boolean refIN,
                          boolean refOUT)
        Calculate CRC checksum.
        **********************************
        ** Pay attention to the data type! **
        **********************************
        The default data type of java is 'int'. If value 'crcInit' has more than 32 bits , remember to add the suffix 'L'
        Parameters:
        rawData - Data to be used to calculate CRC checksum in ArrayList type
        poly - CRC Polynomial
        crcInit - CRC register initial value in long or hex type.
        crcXOROUT - crcXOROUT XOR calculated result to get final CRC
        refIN - Flip per bit of data which to be tested
        refOUT - Flip per bit of data which is after calculation and before XOR output
        Returns:
        CRC value in long type
